{
  "stem": "3331.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, higher grades was when I was four, when I was five.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We started to learn Humash, the Bible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to this schools, this was a one-room school, practically no windows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were sitting and we learned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then till six.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I was six, I started to attend public school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Public school, we had to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there-- this was a Poles and non-Jews-- I mean Poles and Jews, we were together in the same class.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the beginning, it was very hard because the Polish people didn't like Jewish, young Jewish with [INAUDIBLE] And we used to wear yarmulkes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it was a lot of resistance from the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But little by little, we got used to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I went to this public school for seven years, from one grade to the others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And also, after I started the public school, I enter the Talmud Torah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Talmud Torah is a higher class, higher class, in our town that we started to study the Talmud, in the Talmud Torah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in school, I went to school till I was I think 12, 13 years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, later, it was finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was the only-- and I was a very good student in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Even the teachers didn't like Jewish boys because we had [INAUDIBLE] and yarmulkes and we were dressed different.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I always had a very good report cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my report cards were mostly excellent from top to bottom, all subjects, which was very unusual because the teachers didn't like Jewish boys with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they didn't have a choice and they gave me good grades.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In public school, I continued till I finished seventh grades.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
